quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Ɓen ɓe njortaaki hawroyde e amen mbi'i: "Ko hannoo jippinee e makko Maleykaaji ɓen, ma min nji'a Joomi amen?" Gooŋɗii ɓee mawnintinike ka wonkiiji maɓɓe, ɓe townitii townitaare mawnunde."
  25,22,"Ñande ɓe nji'oyta Maleykaaji ɓen weltaare alanaa bonɓe ɓen nden Ñande, ɓe mbi'a: "Heedo heedaango"."
  25,23,"Min ardini faade e ko ɓe ngollunoo kon immorde e gollal, Min mbaɗi ngal punndi saraandi."
  25,24,"Yimɓe aljanna ɓe nden Ñande ɓuri moƴƴude ñiiɓirde ɓuri labeede kadi ñallirde."
  25,25,"E Ñande nde kummu ngun seekorta duule ɗen Malaa'ikaaji ɓen njippinee jippineede."
  25,26,"Laamu goongaawu ngun nden ñalnde ko Hinnorante On ngu woodani, laatoo ñalnde saɗtunde e dow yedduɓe ɓen."
  25,27,"E Ñande tooñɗo on ŋatoyta junngo makko ngon, o wi'a: "Eeh jalla min, mi jogitino wond'ude e Nulaaɗo on Laawol."
  25,28,"Eeh bone am haaniino min, mi njogitanooki kaariijo sehilaajo."
  25,29,"Gooŋɗii o majjinii lam gaayi deftere nden ɓaawo nde arii a am, Seytaane laatike ko o jaasinoowo neɗɗaŋke on."
  25,30,"Nulaaɗo on maaka: "eeyma Jooma pellet, yimɓe am ɓen ɓe njogitike ndee Alqur'aanaare wikkaande(accaande)"."
  25,31,"Ko wano nii, Min mbaɗirani kala Annabaajo gaño immorde e bonɓe ɓen, Joomi maaɗa yonii peewnoowo e ballo."
  25,32,"Ɓeen yedduɓe mbi'i: "Ko hanno Alqur'aanaare nden jippinee e makko e jumla gooto?" Ɗuum ko wano nii, fii yo Min tabintinir nde ɓernde maaɗa nden Min rewnindira nde rewnindirgol."